\c 3
\s Johwani Mubhabhatidzi unoparidza rubhabhatidzo rwokutendeuka
\p
\v 1 Zvino negore regumi namashanu rokutonga kwaTibherio Kesari, Pontio Pirato ari mutongi weJudhiya, Herodhe ari mumwe wavatongi vana veGariri, Firipi munun'una wake, ari mumwe wavatongi vana veIturea nedunhu reTrakoniti, Risanio ari mutongi weAbhirene,
\v 2 Anasi naKayafasi vari vapristi vakuru, shoko raMwari rakasvika kunaJohwani mwanakomana waZakaria murenje.
\v 3 Iye akasvika munyika yose yakapoteredza yaJoridani, akaparidza rubhabhatidzo rwokutendeuka kuti kuve nekukangamwirwa kwezvivi;
\v 4 sezvazvakanyorwa mubhuku ramashoko aIsaya muporofita zvichinzi: Inzwi rounodana murenje \add richiti\add*: Gadzirai nzira yaShe, ruramisai migwagwa yake.
\v 5 Mipata yose ichafusirwa, makomo ose nezvikomo zvose zvichaderedzwa; zvakakombama zvicharuramiswa, nzira dzamakwiringwindi dzienzaniswe;
\v 6 uye nyama yose ichavona ruponeso rwaMwari.
\v 7 Naizvozvo wakati kuchaunga chaibudira kuzobhabhatidzwa naye: Vana venyoka, ndianiko wakakuyambirai kuti mutize kutsamwa kunouya?
\v 8 Naizvozvo berekai zvibereko zvakafanira kutendeuka; musatanga kureva mumoyo menyu, muchiti: Tina Abhurahamu baba \add vedu\add*; nokuti ndinoti kwamuri: Mwari unogona kubva pamabwe awa kumutsira Abhurahamu vana.
\v 9 Zvinovo sanhu ratoiswa pamudzi wemiti; naizvozvo muti mumwe nomumwe usingabereki chibereko chakanaka, unotemerwa pasi, ukandirwe mumoto.
\v 10 Chaunga chikamubvunza, chichiti: Zvino todiniko?
\v 11 Akapindura akati kwavari: Une nguvo mbiri, ngaagovane nousina; nounezvokudya ngaaite saizvozvo.
\v 12 Zvino kwakauyavo vateresi kuzobhabhatidzwa, vakati kwaari: Mudzidzisi, toiteiko?
\v 13 Akati kwavari: Musareva kupfuura pamakatemerwa napo.
\v 14 Namautovo akamubvunza, achiti: Ko isu todiniko? Akati kwaari: Musatyityidzira munhu kana kupomera munhu nhema; uye migutsikane nemubairo wenyu.
\v 15 Zvino vanhu vakati vachatarisira, vose vachirangarira mumoyo mavo pamusoro paJohwani, kuti zvimwe ndiKrustu,
\v 16 Johwani akapindura achiti kunavose: Ini zvirokwazvo ndinokubhabhatidzai nemvura; asi mumwe unesimba kupfuvureni unovuya, wandisina kufanira kusunungura rukanda rweshangu dzake; iye uchakubhabhatidzai neMweya mutsvene nemoto.
\v 17 Rusero rwake \add rwuri\add* muruvoko rwake; uchanatsa kwazvo buriro rake; uye uchavunganidza zviyo mudura rake, asi hundi iye uchaipisa nemoto usingadzimwi.
\v 18 Uye mukukurudzira kwake nezvinhu zvizhinji, akaparidzira vanhu evhangeri.
\v 19 Asi Herodhe mutongi wechina, wakati asvorwa naye pamusoro paHerodhiasi, mukadzi womunun'una wake, nezvakaipa zvose zvaakanga zvaitwa naHerodhe,
\v 20 wakawedzerazve pamusoro pezvose nezvizvi, kuti wakapfigira Johwani mutirongo.
\s Kubhabhatidzwa kwaJesu
\p
\v 21 Zvino zvakaitika \add kuti\add* vanhu vose vabhabhatidzwa, naJesuvo abhabhatidzwa, achinyengetera, denga rakazarurwa.
\v 22 Mweya Mutsvene akaburukira pamusoro pake nechimiro chomuviri sowenjiva, inzwi rikabva kudenga, richiti: Ndiwe Mwanakomana wangu, unodikamwa; wandinofadzwa naye kwazvo.
\s Rudzi rwaJesu Kristu
\p
\v 23 Zvino iye Jesu wakanga achitanga kusvika makore anenge makumi matatu, ari sezvaifungidzirwa, mwanakomana waJosefa, wakanga ari waHeri,
\v 24 wakanga ari waMatati, wakanga ari waRevhi, wakanga ari waMeriki, wakanga ari waJanasi, wakanga ari waJosefa,
\v 25 wakanga ari waMatatiasi, wakanga ari waAmosi, wakanga ari waNaumi, wakanga ari waEsiri, wakanga ari waNagai,
\v 26 wakanga ari waMaati, wakanga ari waMatatiasi, wakanga ari waSimeyini, wakanga ari waJosefa, wakanga ari waJudha,
\v 27 wakanga ari waJohwanani, wakanga ari waResa, wakanga ari waZerubhabheri, wakanga ari waSaratieri, wakanga ari waNeri,
\v 28 wakanga ari waMeriki, wakanga ari waAdhi, wakanga ari waKosamu, wakanga ari waErimodhamu, wakanga ari waEri,
\v 29 wakanga ari waJose, wakanga ari waEriazeri, wakanga ari waJorimu, wakanga ari waMatati, wakanga ari waRevhi,
\v 30 wakanga ari waSimiyoni, wakanga ari waJudha, wakanga ari waJosefa, wakanga ari waJonanu, wakanga ari waEriakimu,
\v 31 wakanga ari waMerea, wakanga ari waMenani, wakanga ari waMatata, wakanga ari waNatatani, wakanga ari waDhavhidhi,
\v 32 wakanga ari waJese, wakanga ari waObhedhi, wakanga ari waBhowazi, wakanga ari waSarimoni, wakanga ari waNaasoni,
\v 33 wakanga ari waAminadhabhi, wakanga ari waAramu, wakanga ari waEziromi, wakanga ari waFaresi, wakanga ari waJudha,
\v 34 wakanga ari waJakobho, wakanga ari waIsaka, wakanga ari waAbhurahamu, wakanga ari waTera, wakanga ari waNahori,
\v 35 wakanga ari waSerugi, wakanga ari waRagau, wakanga ari waFareki, wakanga ari waEberi, wakanga ari waSarah,
\v 36 wakanga ari waKainani, wakanga ari waArifakisadhi, wakanga ari waSemu, wakanga ari waNowa, wakanga ari waRameki,
\v 37 wakanga ari waMatusara, wakanga ari waEnoki, wakanga ari waJaredhi, wakanga ari waMarereeri, wakanga ari waKainani,
\v 38 wakanga ari waEnosi, wakanga ari waSeti, wakanga ari waAdhamu, wakanga ari waMwari.
